{"tid":747244,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人返咗新工,先覺得舊工其實唔錯？然後返舊公司","createTime":"2018-07-18T08:33:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T02:18:16.000Z","uid":143241,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"687c9d9d2048a4d3349ae70c6dbc85f6e3c69774","tid":747244,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T08:33:55.000Z","msg":"當初走嘅原因係因為我有個念頭困擾我好耐同有個同事好閪,不過佢quit喇！個念頭就係想試下由飲食轉做保安,但做咗兩日覺得好難捱,驚做得耐變廢人所以quit咗,之後走返去做包,但新公司原來冇嘢學,祗不過係中央工場將啲麵團打起冷凍之後送嚟舖頭,之後先發酵落料再入爐焗.<br />\n反而舊公司就真係日日打麵團,之後即整.雖然係咁,但返而仲hea過新公司.<br />\n亦因爲咁我聯絡返舊公司個上司,佢話我返去都okay,反正以前個位都未請到人.<br />\n<br />\n但老母係典型奴性心態,認為唔應該成日轉工,話我唔適應咁樣,但其實啱唔啱做落去得我先知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,反而同細路傾就冇呢個問題,佢自己都話職場都係嚟嚟去去,冇話打死同一份工呢啲心態,可能呢啲就係代溝喇.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有冇人都係好似我咁？"},{"pid":"04813197b39788a7cf7e9ee19dc51e7af56a7439","tid":747244,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T09:00:05.000Z","msg":"大家有冇類似嘅經歷？"},{"pid":"82bc0c3e3a949e400b658b77d123d4a374680ee1","tid":747244,"uid":56873,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T09:17:22.000Z","msg":"返la  <br />\n識friend食回頭草。因為要work life balance"},{"pid":"65fc00b15acb26302ac878ab8ca8fb29e4caa87b","tid":747244,"uid":12075,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T09:18:27.000Z","msg":"好草不怕回頭吃"},{"pid":"f91cbcb541e90423cbf59a3b516e1a05cc5dac28","tid":747244,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65fc00b15acb26302ac878ab8ca8fb29e4caa87b","tid":747244,"uid":12075,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T09:18:27.000Z","msg":"好草不怕回頭吃"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T09:28:09.000Z","msg":"老老實實,其實最後嗰個月都好後悔,仲要啱走先開始同新同事friend緊.我以前仲喺道做嗰陣都有人食回頭草,佢以前仲要係喺酒店做嘅添."},{"pid":"6cb4275d9885d03c63dc939b785fb0614dd51bd9","tid":747244,"uid":150053,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T09:30:10.000Z","msg":"反正你都問咗舊公司, 咪返去囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06755bdc7e1fa2b4520dbbf4e9ea4c801a7d1392","tid":747244,"uid":143241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T10:48:54.000Z","msg":"唉,有時做人都幾煩.以為辭咗職搵另一份會好過依家,點知做落又唔係咁理想.反而返新工先覺得舊公司其實好好做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95d0730eee2c1eb51dfa90b0db950ebc0526795f","tid":747244,"uid":8171,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-18T11:13:13.000Z","msg":"返到就返啦，做生不如做熟。最慘係想返又返唔到啫"},{"pid":"81c621536f3d3664976328b41fe09b0e651ce95f","tid":747244,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:44:42.000Z","msg":"太好了,舊上司話可以同上面傾.有機會拎返以前嘅人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e72e9cee2b9147ee12156a42319d120d01d6dd18","tid":747244,"uid":44607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:52:48.000Z","msg":"好馬不吃回頭草"},{"pid":"f034543e13ae0d812e533cc9eb8d6e107962f90f","tid":747244,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e72e9cee2b9147ee12156a42319d120d01d6dd18","tid":747244,"uid":44607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T06:52:48.000Z","msg":"好馬不吃回頭草"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T08:26:06.000Z","msg":"&nbsp;好草不怕回頭吃"},{"pid":"2d05fd841493269b0db764c4dff2319d3887f5ae","tid":747244,"uid":17866,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T08:28:22.000Z","msg":"大把啦<br />\n<br />\n總之凡事留一線"},{"pid":"14991f1c6c4ef17d42eb9eb85561c1409e29c84a","tid":747244,"uid":83799,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T00:36:28.000Z","msg":"如果佢未請到人<br />\n其實佢都頭痛緊<br />\n<br />\n難得有個熟手主動返黎做<br />\n佢又唔使煩人手<br />\n又唔使再花時間教人<br />\n對佢黎講都係好事<br />\n你又做到想做嘅事<br />\nWin win雙贏<br />\nWhy not?"},{"pid":"d740de552a71902a9b9b67a643a169e2a8fe7dcf","tid":747244,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"14991f1c6c4ef17d42eb9eb85561c1409e29c84a","tid":747244,"uid":83799,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T00:36:28.000Z","msg":"如果佢未請到人<br />\n其實佢都頭痛緊<br />\n<br />\n難得有個熟手主動返黎做<br />\n佢又唔使煩人手<br />\n又唔使再花時間教人<br />\n對佢黎講都係好事<br />\n你又做到想做嘅事<br />\nWin win雙贏<br />\nWhy not?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T04:08:22.000Z","msg":"上頭話畀我返去,我仲可以拎返走之前嘅人工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b529403f292e8167ce8c5cae89aa892955e0df7f","tid":747244,"uid":168674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T04:11:20.000Z","msg":"好馬不食回頭草 你走過 上面一定唔會升你先 你自己諗"},{"pid":"8e7b37ccc9f06a5e79e12d64b92886aebce8e7cc","tid":747244,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b529403f292e8167ce8c5cae89aa892955e0df7f","tid":747244,"uid":168674,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T04:11:20.000Z","msg":"好馬不食回頭草 你走過 上面一定唔會升你先 你自己諗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T04:33:46.000Z","msg":"我從來唔覺得自己係隻好馬,我不過係隻斑馬啫.至少食回頭草其實冇問題,我公司有人喺酒店做過都返嚟做啦,出嚟做嘢都係為錢,第二就係睇下工作環境啱唔啱自己啫.<br />\n舊時我做麥記嗰陣雖然好撚忙,但我做得好開心.<br />\n其實做得我嗰行啊,有本錢嘅都諗住自己開舖做老闆㗎喇,同人打工做到幾叻咪又係得個朵叫師傅."},{"pid":"ec89b0336fe8f8952a059188022a0e39586f163f","tid":747244,"uid":844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:09:36.000Z","msg":"返啦"},{"pid":"d63f89af98f8b760e47709f0d3ed8f6b4b9f3ce8","tid":747244,"uid":43483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:19:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8366bf4db574c78b1f3ccccb21556edef091a6cd","tid":747244,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ec89b0336fe8f8952a059188022a0e39586f163f","tid":747244,"uid":844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:09:36.000Z","msg":"返啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T07:49:16.000Z","msg":"返到啊,8月返去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家呢份返埋下星期五就收皮,反正未夠一個月,但啲人就當我會長做咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n呢間人工又低過我舊公司2000蚊,嘢又冇舊公司多嘢學,但就有由開工做到收工,想去廁所蛇下都難,個6日假仲要三個月後先有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a34d6625b225ca54124b194bb37a63b816f3d09","tid":747244,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d63f89af98f8b760e47709f0d3ed8f6b4b9f3ce8","tid":747244,"uid":43483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:19:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T07:50:25.000Z","msg":"喺舊公司得罪人？"},{"pid":"73e20b7c9bd1247f529b4d10d924da8a4ae3b4fb","tid":747244,"uid":43483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4a34d6625b225ca54124b194bb37a63b816f3d09","tid":747244,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d63f89af98f8b760e47709f0d3ed8f6b4b9f3ce8","tid":747244,"uid":43483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T05:19:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T07:50:25.000Z","msg":"喺舊公司得罪人？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T10:03:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90bd5929d439584a4e99cd3332433105e7605328","tid":747244,"uid":102956,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T16:42:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"982d2b5883f2cbf64258f5a68ed0c2f2a2e284f0","tid":747244,"uid":172733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T16:46:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拿返舊人工就開心？"},{"pid":"9289dcd217dd68ff961ca5a84f1a8625cbdf0649","tid":747244,"uid":43483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"982d2b5883f2cbf64258f5a68ed0c2f2a2e284f0","tid":747244,"uid":172733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T16:46:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拿返舊人工就開心？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T06:02:55.000Z","msg":"咁相對既姐<br />\n如果新工多唔多又惡頂幾倍真係做生不如做熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f39627b0e0612fb0bda68c2c647881aea227f8be","tid":747244,"uid":143241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9289dcd217dd68ff961ca5a84f1a8625cbdf0649","tid":747244,"uid":43483,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"982d2b5883f2cbf64258f5a68ed0c2f2a2e284f0","tid":747244,"uid":172733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-21T16:46:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 拿返舊人工就開心？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T06:02:55.000Z","msg":"咁相對既姐<br />\n如果新工多唔多又惡頂幾倍真係做生不如做熟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-22T13:41:13.000Z","msg":"啱啊,我喺新公司由開工做到收工,停低一秒唞下氣都會畀人話做乜停低,做咗一個禮拜,原本諗過做埋下個禮拜先辭職唞兩日返舊公司,但諗諗下都係再做廢青多一個禮拜先.<br />\n呢個用夾埋做得嗰9日嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}